  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study factors (drugs, serum concentration of drugs,
      nutrition, physical activity, demographics, diseases etc.) related to constipation and
      diarrhea in nursing homes, and the effect of different laxative regimens.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
